outputs.output_descr: In the framework of the Public Private Partnership signed between UNDP and ChevronTexaco in November 2002, this Preparatory Assistance document will provide the legal framework for the design and launching of the Angola Enterprise Programme (AEP) that will support an enhanced access to financial and non-financial business development services for micro, small and medium size enterprises in Angola. The AEP will focus on investments in vocational training, microfinance, business development services and business incubators.
